HOTAI MOTOR CO April Sales Fall 53.40% (Table) : 2207 TT

-- B y   J a n e t   O n g
-- 
2011-05-10T10:37:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-10/hotai-motor-co-april-sales-fall-53-40-table-2207-tt.html
HOTAI MOTOR CO said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 53.40% to NT$3,334,660,000 from NT$7,156,204,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2011           4/2010
Sales           3,334,660        7,156,204   
YOY%             -53.40%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           30,409,797       28,861,119  
YOY%              5.37%  
=================================================================
 